rows.label: tlk45100152_01_msg0001
rows.name: Have you ever seen Emperor Nefer?

rows.label: tlk45100152_01_msg0002
rows.name:
He's not much older than me, but
he rules over all of Superbia.

rows.label: tlk45100152_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Only thing I ever looked after is
my pet Pilehorn Rhino Beetle...

rows.label: tlk45100152_01_msg0004
rows.name:
But this guy's looking after a whole
country! Isn't that amazing?

rows.label: tlk45100152_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I just wish my mom would stop
comparing me to him...
